overview: Recorded at the iconic Olympia Theatre in Dublin ‘Changed’ was a show over 2 years in the making. With hilarious stories of financial stupidity and both sexual & spiritual awakening Paul walks us through the many ways he’s changed since his last full show.  Luckily though none of these events have changed how funny he is. With over 70 minutes of never before seen material don’t miss this highly acclaimed performance from one of the UK’s most popular comedians.
title: Paul Smith - Changed Tour 2020 - 2021
